{"tid":2358485,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李永達引述黎智英：在最困難時間撐住","createTime":"2021-01-08T07:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T07:59:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0367d54998666251bc49a717263bfc59046fd3","tid":2358485,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/F5VR6C5FWJGSFLFLR7VCOXSDVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FF5VR6C5FWJGSFLFLR7VCOXSDVE%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIclSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=b937b013\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2FF5VR6C5FWJGSFLFLR7VCOXSDVE%2F&h=288e5c07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/F5VR6C5FWJGSFLFLR7VCOXSDVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n李永達引述黎智英：在最困難時間撐住<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方國安處前日動員千警大搜捕53名泛民人士，轟動全港，昨晨民主黨成員李永達及劉慧卿到荔枝角收押所探望被控欺詐和勾結外國勢力、未審先囚的壹傳媒創辦人黎智英。劉慧卿指三人曾談論警方大搜捕行動，以及美國國會一度被示威者佔領的事件。李永達其後於facebook發文，轉述黎智英所言，「希望大家要在最困難的時間撐住」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：各方打氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JrIa6Gf5AI2Qdn3pW53YJu03s0o=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K7W5TPVZBJBRXMMZ4MCHCY5PZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJrIa6Gf5AI2Qdn3pW53YJu03s0o%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK7W5TPVZBJBRXMMZ4MCHCY5PZY.jpg&h=f6cf97d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉慧卿及李永達昨晨到荔枝角收押所探望黎智英，逗留約一小時後離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與劉慧卿探望 談大搜捕泛民<br />\n<br />\n黎智英自除夕夜再遭還柙至今已九天。昨早8時許，民主黨前主席劉慧卿。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至中午，李永達在facebook發文，指黎智英精神很好，會面中黎已得悉警方拘捕53名泛民人士，他轉述黎智英寄語港人，「希望大家要在最困難的時間撐住」，黎亦感謝市民對他的支持，揚言「會繼續頂住」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ww1jzc_FviV9nqLEkO4XgC4Wr5s=/2331x2048/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KLIJ5CRNZVA6XFUO3YRJZS365A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fww1jzc_FviV9nqLEkO4XgC4Wr5s%3D%2F2331x2048%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKLIJ5CRNZVA6XFUO3YRJZS365A.JPG&h=cf20fc9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英還柙至今已九日，昨由懲教員押送步往會面室。"},{"pid":"232115366c2557c33310a7dd81630b21cca269e2","tid":2358485,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f100031983547fb89df172ff4b9562aa8b577b","tid":2358485,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:59:04.000Z","msg":"黎生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0729e81e152d9a4c0b10c4dc7520d1543d4b0d12","tid":2358485,"uid":156109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:59:09.000Z","msg":"哇四方西"}]}